data.name: richTextBox_description.Text
data.value:
This is a software used to calculate the available host address of a IPv4 or IPv6 address/range.
How to use: - Directly fill the IP to be calculated in the text box.
Version 1(2022-07-25) - First Version
Version 1.1(2022-08-01) - Add wildcard mask in ipv4 result.
